title: Prabowo Subianto - Wikipedia
snippet: Prabowo Subianto Djojohadikusumo (born 17 October 1951) is an Indonesian politician, businessman, and retired military officer who has served as the eighth president of Indonesia since 2024. He previously served as the 26th minister of defense under President Joko Widodo from 2019 to 2024.

title: Prabowo Subianto | Biography, Career, & Facts | Britannica
snippet: Prabowo Subianto (born October 17, 1951, Jakarta, Indonesia) is a former general of the Indonesian army and businessman who is now president of Indonesia (2024– ).
